               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa kidāna mǝḥrat “Book of the Covenant of Mercy” (fols.
                     3ra-50rb)
 II) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 3 miracles (fols.
                     50rb-56vb)
 III) Malkǝʾa kidāna mǝḥrat “Image of the Covenant of Mercy”
                     (57ra-64rb) (cp. Malkǝʾa gubaʾe, ʾAśmära 1948 E.C., pp. 63-73)
 
                     Additio 1.</summary>
