               <provenance>Different persons are mentioned in
                     supplication formulas throughout the Ms.: Tawalda Madḫǝn (e.g., 12va), Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer (e.g., 22rb), Ṣǝllatä Muse (e.g., 22rb), Walatta Madḫǝn (e.g., 33vb),
                     Walda Māryām (e.g., 30va), Romḥa Śǝllāse (e.g.,
                        35vb), Walatta Ḥǝywat (e.g., 35vb), ʾAmata Mikāʾel (e.g., 37vb), Walda Krǝstos (e.g., 47rb).</provenance></history>
